moe.wyv.Sad_Bot

Class Channel

  • java.lang.Object
    • moe.wyv.Sad_Bot.Channel

  • public class Channel
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains all the statistics on viewers. This class currently uses Java data structures, but will eventually be changed to use a SQL database. The methods reflect this.
    Author:
    fettuccine

      • getUserForced

        public User getUserForced(java.lang.String username)
        Retrieves a user from the database, even if they don't exist. A new user entry will be created. CAREFUL! Most of the time we need to get a user, we know the user is in the chat for one reason or another. The only time this shouldn't be used is if one user is looking for information about another user.
        Parameters:
        username - name of user
        Returns:
        user if they exist, otherwise generates a new user
